
Introduction
------------
Inotify is on erlang port for the Linux inotify API allowing one to monitor
changes to files and directory in the filesystem.

Installation
------------
If building from git:

$ ./rebar compile

If using as a dependency in another rebar project add this snippet to the projects
rebar.config:

  {deps, [
        ... other dependencies ...
        {inotify, ".*", {git, "https://github.com/sheyll/inotify.git"}}]}

